==票房==

===争议===
[[File:Movie_hundred_group_battle,in_Nanjing,20150831,03.jpg|thumb]]
2015年8月29日，网络上出现有关院线票房的政治任务，以及9月3日前票房不分账，票款全归院线和影院的消息。有网友公布手写或者经过涂改的票根，称该电影[[偷票房|偷票房]]。电影局否认传闻，称七部委下达文件希望各地组织当地党团员集体观看电影，但会坚决抵制和制止偷票房行为。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/15/0830/12/B293I2CL00031H2L.html |title="百团大战"挪票房？电影局回应:若属实严肃处理 |access-date=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2020-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200503035134/http://ent.163.com/15/0830/12/B293I2CL00031H2L.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.huxiu.com/article/124640 |title=与《百团大战》同档很悲催，华谊博纳老总暗示票房被“偷” |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924031937/http://www.huxiu.com/article/124640 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.163.com/15/0830/16/B29H7D6J0001124J.html |title=《百团大战》被指偷票房 官方:党员观影群体庞大 |access-date=2015-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150902001040/http://news.163.com/15/0830/16/B29H7D6J0001124J.html |archive-date=2015-09-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/15/0901/08/B2DOU4OA000300B1.html |language= |title=《百团大战》排片不及《烈日灼心》 票房却高3成 |publisher=法制晚报 |date=2015-09-01 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150903023708/http://ent.163.com/15/0901/08/B2DOU4OA000300B1.html |archive-date=2015-09-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/15/0831/05/B2ARB58G00032DGD.html |language= |title=网曝《百团大战》腾挪票房 |publisher=东南快报(福州) |date=2015-08-31 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202225357/http://ent.163.com/15/0831/05/B2ARB58G00032DGD.html |archive-date=2016-02-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

